<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, January 26 (Xinhua) -- Former member of Hong Kong's
Executive Council Chung Sze-yuen says he would do his best to
assist Hong Kong special Administrative Region (HKSAR) Chief
Executive Tung Chee Hwa in making government policies.
</P>
