<BODY>
<HEADLINE> ANC Denies Having Endorsed Mercenary Activities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, January 26 (Xinhua) -- South Africa's ruling
African National Congress (ANC) today denied its endorsement of any
form of mercenary activity in the African continent.
</P>
<P>
