was reportedly equipped with machine guns, grenade launchers,
seven helicopters, eight airplanes and even two Russia-made
Mig-27 fighters.
</P>
<P>
And at present, "Executive Outcomes" has expanded its
activities beyond military-style operations and is set to become
a behind-the-scene political player in Africa. 
