stability;
</P>
<P>
-- a fight against poverty "through improvement of decent and
civilized living standards of the people, materially and
spiritually."
</P>
<P>
Chea Sim reiterated his party's adherence to the principle of
promoting a multi-party and liberal democratic system and respect
for human rights.
</P>
<P>
The CPP Extraordinary General Assembly began on January 24,
with participation by 705 delegates. 
