city" in China, last year attracted 94 new ROK-funded enterprises,
accounting for 79 percent of the total number of newly-introduced
foreign-funded enterprises in the city.
</P>
<P>
"ROK has become the most important trading partner of
Weihai", the official said, "Last year the city's trade volume
with ROK reached 852 million US dollars, a 35 percent increase
over the previous year".
</P>
<P>
The nearest distance between Weihai to ROK, which face each
other across the sea, is less than 100 nautical miles. 
