industrialization and urbanization in the province. To attract
more investment to Sichuan, the provincial government has issued
the Regulation on Management of Development Zones in Sichuan
Province
</P>
<P>
According to the new rules, an inspection and assessment system
for development zones will be set up, and those development zones
that does score due progress in construction will not receive
preferential treatment in the future. 
